Interface StoreIterator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<KeyValuePair>

    public interface StoreIterator
extends java.util.Iterator<KeyValuePair>
    This class represents an iterator over the contents of a Store. It doesn't have any methods of its own other than the ones from the Iterator interface Each key and value in the iteration are represented by a KeyValuePair
